authors: Kebisek, Julianna; Forrest, Lanna J; Maule, Alexis L; Steelman, Ryan A; Ambrose, John F
title: Special report: Prevalence of selected underlying health conditions among active component Army service members with coronavirus disease 2019, 11 February-6 April 2020
sample: COVID-19 has been a reportable condition for the Department of Defense since 5 February 2020, and, as of the morning of 6 April, a total of 873 cases were reported to the Disease Reporting System internet from Army installations.

title: Returning to Play after Prolonged Training Restrictions in Professional Collision Sports
sample: The COVID-19 pandemic in 2020 has resulted in widespread training disruption in many sports.
